cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Settlers of Mars in teaching or research, please cite it as below."
title: "Settlers of Mars & D&D Role Player Adventure: The Gateway to Space Science Mastery"
abstract: >-
  An open educational game that blends the resource-management mechanics of
  Settlers of Catan with Dungeons & Dragons role-play and a browser colony sim,
  to teach space biology, biotechnology, and aerospace engineering. Includes
  3D-printable board pieces (STL), AI "Space Wizard" Dungeon-Master prompt
  templates, example board layouts, and a companion browser game (Lunar &
  Martian Frontier).
type: software
